title: [Coastal Cliffs, Small Hillock]
description: From here you can see the white-capped moonlit waves of the Darkstone far below and to the north, and the hazy, blue-grey mountains' rising peaks to the south.
From here you can see the brilliant white-capped sapphire waves of the Darkstone far below and to the north, and the hazy, blue-grey mountains' rising peaks to the south.
